   }, [conversation.timeline, filter, searchTerm]);
   ```

**End Result of Phase 4:** A fully interactive, visually rich conversation viewer that makes the most of the structured timeline data. Users can expand tool calls to see exact file changes, toggle agent thoughts, filter by event type, and navigate large conversations efficiently.

